作用 | 命名成 `.bis.ts` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":102,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":103,"content":"硬门禁：`STUDIO-STRUCT-021`～`024`。本批每完成一域，须从 `studio-v2-layering-baseline.json` **移除已合规文件**（或整表重扫后只剩未迁域）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":104,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"删除确认、FormModal 开合可为组件瞬时态。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":124,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"### 3.5 调试器","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":126,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":127,"content":"- Session 快照、Board 摘要、mailbox 未读等进 `debugger` store。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":128,"content":"- mock 数据经 bis/ajaxProxy，**禁止** `DebuggerShell` 直引 mock 模块当长期真源。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":129,"content":"- 不在本批强制 Host 全真会话（与现调试范围一致）；结构先对齐。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":130,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":131,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":133,"content":"## 4. 刀序与依赖","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":134,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":135,"content":"```text","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":136,"content":"V2-LY-0   约定 Provider / 空 shellBis 骨架（可与 B 合并）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":137,"content":"V2-LY-1～4  故事编辑器（双层 + 拆 shell/feature + 保存 flush + 出 baseline）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":138,"content":"V2-LY-5～6  角色库","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumbe