{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-3dfc1a24-3a78-4212-b40a-3afcc7506db3-38\nfc_1b5f2a8d-eae4-98d2-aa53-8b9f00451c44_4","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"debugger|调试","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md","contextAfter":5,"caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-3dfc1a24-3a78-4212-b40a-3afcc7506db3-38\nfc_1b5f2a8d-eae4-98d2-aa53-8b9f00451c44_4","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"debugger|调试","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":3,"content":"相关：[05](./05-技术选型与工程边界.md) · [18](./18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md) · [03](../需求/03-编辑器界面需求.md) · [04](../需求/04-调试器界面需求.md) · [V2 目录 09](../sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md) · [V2 门禁 08](../sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/08-Studio-V2前端工程规则与质量门禁需求.md)","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":4,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":5,"content":"> **定稿哲学：** Store 只是账本；Shell 负责灌账本；Feature bis 负责动作；UI 只读展示并调 bis。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":6,"content":"> 该分层已在 SlimVID 等系统验证；本仓 Studio V2 **采用同一套**，不另发明状态框架。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":7,"content":"> **Zustand ≠ Profile/Memory 真源**；真源永远在 Next → EngineHost → `data/`。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":8,"content":"> **规则文件：** [.cursor/rules/studio-v2-client-layering.mdc](../../.cursor/rules/studio-v2-client-layering.mdc)。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":51,"content":"| Studio Zustand | **否**（UI 工作副本 / 加载态 / 调试快照缓存） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":52,"content":"| 浏览器 | 只发意图 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":53,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":54,"content":"## 3. Shell","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":55,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"每个有独立数据生命周期的页面，**有且仅有一个** `useXxxShellBis`（落 `src/bis/shellBis/`，文件名 `*.shell.bis.ts`）：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"| 灌列表 / 灌调试快照 / 灌编辑会话 | 处理每个按钮业务 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":62,"content":"| 监听 `*RefreshStamp` 触发有界刷新 | 代替 Feature bis |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"| generation + AbortController 防竞态 | 跨页乱写无关 domain store |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":64,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":65,"content":"### v1 Shell 清单（Studio V2）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":66,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":72,"content":"| `useDebuggerShellBis` | `/debugger` | Session 快照、Board、mailbox 等 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":73,"content":"| `useCharactersShellBis` 等 | 各库页 | 列表 + 选中摘要 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":74,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":75,"content":"仅 `*.shell.bis.ts`（及少数 `*Flow.ts`）可碰 **路由导航**。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":76,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":77,"content":"## 4. Feature bis","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":92,"content":"- 按域：`src/stores/<domain>/`（characters / storyEditor / debugger / packages…）  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":93,"content":"- `zustand` + 可选 Context Provider；订阅 `useStore` + shallow  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":94,"content":"- **禁止**把各页业务切片堆进单一上帝 store；全局壳仅极薄偏好（如 workspace 标题）  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":95,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"Write action **结果型命名**：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":97,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":182,"content":"| CallSession | debugger shell 灌快照；挂机后清空 session 切片 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":183,"content":"| SSE 聊天 | feature bis 管流；store 只留 streaming 标志 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":184,"content":"| canvas.layout | 画布运行时 + flush 进 editor store；引擎忽略 layout |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":185,"content":"| Memory | 不进大数组；短查询经 API |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":186,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":187,"content":"## 10. 落地顺序","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":199,"content":"- [ ] 列表/调试/编辑会话由 shell 灌入对应 domain store  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":200,"content":"- [ ] 编辑器保存前 flush；配置态不靠 page hook 自管  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":201,"content":"- [ ] `check:studio-structure` 含 021～024 绿（baseline 仅覆盖未触碰存量）  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":202,"content":"- [ ] Zustand 不当 Profile/Memory 真源  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":46,"totalMatchedLines":7,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-3dfc1a24-3a78-4212-b40a-3afcc7506db3-38\nfc_1b5f2a8d-eae4-98d2-aa53-8b9f00451c44_4","startedAtMs":"1784855198282","completedAtMs":"1784855198566"},"model_call_id":"d28447b4-77e3-438d-a341-52a7d1fc3a05-7-5ogp","session_id":"945260ce-2ae4-4b00-a3dd-28691eb52a31","timestamp_ms":1784855198533}
